[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0865","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0865.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0591","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 事件日志权限配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 事件日志存在不恰当的访问权限配置漏洞，本地普通用户可能能够读取或清除安全事件日志记录。攻击者可利用此漏洞获取系统敏感信息，或在入侵后清理日志痕迹以规避检测。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限方可利用此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0591"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.650","remediation":"限制 %SystemRoot%\\System32\\config\\ 目录下 AppEvent.evt、SecEvent.evt、SysEvent.evt 文件的访问权限，仅允许 SYSTEM 和 Administrators 组读取。升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本以彻底修复权限配置问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0591","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0591","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-05xx/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/justakazh/CVE_Database/blob/06bd07f32c89b43f30d59ff450dfbb661e471cbe/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/b13a5af37e59aa19fd1ac1c09247642e81435453/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0591.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/e75163879b5629a697822216993d714626893061/api/1999/CVE-1999-0591.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0865.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0862","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0862.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0589","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表权限漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中关键注册表项存在权限配置不当漏洞，攻击者利用不安全的注册表权限可修改系统关键配置，进而实现本地权限提升或完全控制系统。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限或通过远程获取写入权限后进行利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0589"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.410","remediation":"使用 regedt32.exe 检查并收紧系统关键注册表项（如 HKLM\\SAM、HKLM\\SECURITY、HKLM\\SYSTEM）的 ACL 权限，确保仅 SYSTEM 和 Administrators 拥有完全控制权，移除 Everyone 组的写入权限。同时安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 及后续安全汇总更新，并在域环境中通过组策略统一加固注册表权限配置。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0589","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0589.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/CVEDB/Poc-Git/blob/0275aeb329b0747c9a1d46160c921eae06095557/1999/CVE-1999-0589.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0589","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/97009c469920f4d8991128f84d19644c3badca15/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-05xx/CVE-1999-0589.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0589.md","https://github.com/brenonevs/prs-pentest/blob/001cf17eedeb4aad73618d3140ca1f5dc93e69b3/CVEs & POCs/1999/CVE-1999-0589.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0862.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0860","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0860.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0588","title":"OpenSource Router 分片数据包过滤绕过漏洞","description":"路由器或防火墙的包过滤规则未能正确处理异常的 IP 分片数据包，导致攻击者可通过发送特制的分片包绕过访问控制列表或入侵检测系统。该漏洞允许未经认证的远程攻击者绕过安全策略，可能导致信息泄露或服务不可用，影响运行各类开源路由软件及防火墙系统。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0588"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.290","remediation":"在路由器或防火墙上启用分片包重组与深度检测功能，设置最小分片大小限制，丢弃异常的微小分片包。配置访问控制列表（ACL）对分片包进行精确过滤，防止攻击者利用分片绕过安全策略。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0588","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0588.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0588","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0588.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0588.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0588.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-56r4-8x77-7j27/GHSA-56r4-8x77-7j27.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0588.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0860.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0859","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0859.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0587","title":"OpenSource 应用 WWW 服务器文件系统限制绕过漏洞","description":"WWW 服务器未运行在受限文件系统环境中（如未使用 chroot 机制隔离），导致远程攻击者可通过 HTTP 请求直接访问服务器系统关键文件（如 /etc/passwd、配置文件等），造成敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响未正确配置 chroot 环境的各类 WWW 服务器软件，攻击者无需认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。修复方式为使用 chroot 或容器技术限制 Web 服务的文件系统访问范围。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0587"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.170","remediation":"将 WWW 服务器配置为在 chroot 环境或容器中运行，限制其对 /etc/passwd、/etc/shadow 等系统关键文件的访问。修改 Web 服务器配置文件，设置 DocumentRoot 为独立目录，并禁止符号链接跟随 (FollowSymLinks)，同时使用最小权限原则运行服务进程（如 www-data 用户）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0587","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0587.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0587","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0587.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0587.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0587.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-w7xx-5rj3-rrrc/GHSA-w7xx-5rj3-rrrc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0587.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0859.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0856","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0856.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0586","title":"多厂商 Host Service Port Handler 组件提权漏洞","description":"网络服务运行在非标准端口上可能导致安全隐患，攻击者可能利用该服务绕过防火墙规则和入侵检测系统，进行未授权访问或权限提升。服务端口隐藏可被用作后门或持久化手段，增加安全监控和审计的难度。该漏洞影响使用非标准端口运行网络服务的系统，需通过端口扫描和基线核查进行检测。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0586"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:41.060","remediation":"建立并维护全网资产清单，使用 Nmap 等工具定期扫描所有端口，识别运行在非标准端口的服务。对每项服务核实其业务必要性，记录责任人及用途；未经授权的服务立即停止并移除。在防火墙上配置零信任策略，只放行必要端口并对源 IP 做白名单限制。对必须使用非标准端口的服务，确保其本身经过安全加固并定期审计日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0586","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0586.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0586.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0586","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0586.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0586.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0586.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0586.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86247/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0856.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0853","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0853.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0584","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 文件系统非 NTFS 安全漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统未使用具备访问控制列表（ACL）机制的 NTFS 文件系统，而是采用 FAT16/FAT32 等不支持文件级权限控制的文件系统格式，导致任意本地用户均可绕过权限检查直接读取、修改或删除系统中的敏感文件。由于缺乏文件系统级别的安全隔离机制，攻击者可利用此缺陷实现权限提升或敏感信息泄露，严重影响系统机密性与完整性。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级为严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0584"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.830","remediation":"立即将 Windows NT 系统所在分区的文件系统由 FAT/FAT32 转换为 NTFS（通过 `convert c: /fs:ntfs` 命令完成，无损转换）。NTFS 提供文件级 ACL 权限控制，可防止未授权访问。Windows NT 产品已停止支持，强烈建议升级至 Windows Server 2016/2019/2022 或 Windows 10/11 等受支持版本以获取持续安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/195","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0584.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0584","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0584.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0584.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0584.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x554-2vfc-2px3/GHSA-x554-2vfc-2px3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0584.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86241/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0853.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0851","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0851.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0583","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 域信任关系安全漏洞","description":"Windows NT 域间存在单向或双向信任关系配置安全隐患，远程攻击者可在无需认证且利用复杂度低的情况下，利用域间信任机制突破访问控制边界，从已控制的受信任域向目标域横向移动，通过传递身份验证请求获取目标域资源的未授权访问权限，实现跨域渗透。CVSS v2 评分 10.0，可导致目标系统机密性、完整性和可用性完全受损。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0583"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.710","remediation":"建议立即将 Windows NT 4.0 升级至受支持版本（Windows Server 2019/2022 或更高版本），启用 SID 筛选以防范信任提升攻击。仅在业务必要下建立域信任，并设置为单向而非双向信任，同时为每个信任配置隔离。对所有域控制器持续安装最新安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1284","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0583.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0583","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0583.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0583.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0583.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9r38-2pp7-328c/GHSA-9r38-2pp7-328c.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0583.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86240/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0851.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0848","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0848.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0581","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表权限配置不当漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的 HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT 注册表项存在权限配置不当漏洞，系统关键权限设置不合理，授予了非授权用户过高的访问级别。本地攻击者可利用该缺陷修改系统文件关联或执行配置篡改，进而实现权限提升。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 全系列版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0581"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.473","remediation":"使用 regedt32 修改 HKEY_CLASSES_ROOT 权限，将 Everyone 组的权限从「完全控制」降为「读取」，移除不必要的用户和组。安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 及后续安全更新以限制关键注册表项的默认访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0581","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0581.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dc83b9e6d88de194a14e3020b4e71ac42054e609/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0581.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0581","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0581.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0581.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0581.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0581.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86236/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0848.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0846","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0846.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0580","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表键权限许可和访问控制漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统中 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE 注册表键存在权限配置不当漏洞，该键存储操作系统核心安全与配置信息，但默认权限设置过于宽松，导致未授权用户可读取甚至修改其中的系统关键项。攻击者可利用不当权限访问或篡改 HKLM 下安全策略、服务配置等关键数据，造成敏感信息泄露、权限提升乃至系统完全受控。该漏洞影响全系 Windows NT 操作系统，CVSS v2 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0580"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.357","remediation":"Windows NT 已停止支持，建议升级至 Windows Server 2019/2022 或更高版本。如无法升级，需手动收紧注册表权限：运行 regedt32，展开 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE，右键选择「权限」，移除 Everyone 组的完全控制权，仅保留 SYSTEM 和 Administrators 的读取权限，并应用强制 ACL 继承到所有子项。同时部署组策略限制本地注册表远程访问。作为临时缓解，限制对受影响主机的网络访问并启用注册表审计日志。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0580","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0580.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0580.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0580","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0580.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0580.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0580.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0580.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86248/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0846.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0845","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0845.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0579","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表审核策略日志记录缺失漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统的注册表审计策略存在缺陷，系统未对非关键注册表键的访问事件记录成功或失败的审计日志。该漏洞导致对这些注册表键值的修改、创建或删除操作无法被安全日志捕获，使得管理员无法通过审计日志追踪对非关键注册表项的未授权更改。攻击者可能利用此审计缺失，在未留下可追溯痕迹的情况下修改系统配置或注册表项，降低系统的审计完整性和安全可见性，间接增加了后续攻击活动的隐匿性和成功概率。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0579"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.243","remediation":"建议安装 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 6a 及后续安全更新。通过域安全策略或本地安全策略启用「审计对象访问」，覆盖所有注册表项；针对非关键注册表项手动配置审核条目，如使用注册表编辑器为关键项添加 SYSTEM 审计访问。无法立即修复时部署第三方注册表监控工具（如 Sysinternals Regmon）补充审计缺失。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/228","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0579.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0579","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0579.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0579.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0579.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0579.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86238/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a38c45d0-f252-4969-8539-5c22f5a47cc8.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0845.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0844","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0844.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0578","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 注册表审核策略日志遗漏漏洞","description":"Windows NT 注册表审核策略存在缺陷，系统未能对安全关键注册表键的访问和修改操作记录成功或失败事件日志。本地攻击者可通过修改注册表敏感项绕过安全审计，实施权限提升或系统配置篡改等攻击，且相关操作不会被系统日志记录。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0578"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.117","remediation":"通过注册表编辑器 (regedt32.exe) 对安全关键注册表项（如 HKLM\\SAM、HKLM\\SECURITY、HKLM\\Software\\Microsoft\\Windows NT\\CurrentVersion）启用审核，设置 \"审核策略\" 中的 \"审核对象访问\" 为 \"成功和失败\"。同时使用 Windows NT 资源包中的 auditpol.exe 工具确认审核策略已生效。Windows NT 已停止支持，建议升级至 Windows Server 2008/2012/2019/2022 等受支持版本以获得完整安全审计能力。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/228","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0578.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0578","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0578.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0578.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/04a84e78299e2aeaab4d2594fc26f920778c7b06/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0578.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0578.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x87000/86053/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0844.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0843","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0843.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0577","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 文件审核策略日志记录缺失漏洞","description":"Windows NT 系统文件审核策略存在缺陷，对非关键文件或目录的访问操作（无论成功或失败）均不记录审核事件日志。攻击者利用此缺陷可在不触发审核告警的前提下访问、修改或删除非关键文件资源，绕过安全监控机制。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 及早期版本，CVSS 评分 10.0（严重），属于安全审计绕过类漏洞。攻击条件为本地或远程拥有文件系统访问权限，利用方式为直接操作非关键文件/目录且不留痕迹。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0577"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:40.007","remediation":"tags\n- The content inside <value> will be used as the remediation field\n\nLet me craft a good Chinese remediation suggestion:\n- Upgrade to a modern Windows server version\n- Configure file audit policies properly\n- Provide specific steps and mitigation measures分析：CVE-1999-0577涉及Windows NT系统的文件审计策略未记录非关键文件/目录的成功/失败事件。根据漏洞描述，需要修复Windows NT的日志审计功能。\n\n<value>升级到Windows Server 2003 SP1或更高版本，使用本地安全策略配置“拒绝访问检查”和“成功/失败审计”策略，对于旧系统可通过修改注册表项[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SYSTEM\\CurrentControlSet\\Control\\Lsa]下的Audit基址来启用审计日志记录，如无法立即升级，建议通过组策略强制启用文件审计策略。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0577","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b78238ce198ba9bb84cf32286dd81a9973f793b6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0577.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0577","https://github.